{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-4/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7b9439f3-8506-5b1f-998a-56b969d7376a","excerpt":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus…","html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용</a></li>\n<li><strong>개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus) 적용</strong></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 5 - 블로그(GitHub Pages) 배포</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 6 - 사용자 지정 도메인 적용</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>이번 포스트에서는 개츠비 블로그에 댓글 기능을 적용해 보도록 할게요.\n댓글 기능으로 대표적인 오픈소스로 utterances와 giscus가 있어요.\n저는 GitHub Discussions로 작동하는 댓글 시스템 giscus 오픈소스 앱을 적용하여 방문자가 포스트에 댓글과 반응을 남길 수 있도록 할게요.\n이유는 utterances 보다 giscus가 좀 더 풍부한 옵션을 제공하고 있으며, 최신 버전까지 관리가 잘 되고 있어 많은 사람에게 선택받고 있어요.</p>\n<p>몇 가지 설정을 진행하면 giscus 기능을 적용할 수 있어요. 순서대로 잘 따라해 주세요!</p>\n<h2>1. GitHub Repository 생성</h2>\n<p>giscus는 GitHub Discussions를 이용하기 때문에 레포지토리를 설정해 주어야 해요.\n저는 지금까지 만든 개츠비 블로그를 <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/pages/quickstart\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">GitHub Pages</a>를 이용해서 배포할 거라,\n공식 문서 가이드에 따라 레포지토리를 생성할게요. <a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">깃허브</a>의 내 레포지토리로 접속해서 <strong>New</strong> 버튼을 클릭해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-1] GitHub Repository\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/f058b/repo-new.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/c26ae/repo-new.png 158w,\n/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/6bdcf/repo-new.png 315w,\n/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/f058b/repo-new.png 630w,\n/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/40601/repo-new.png 945w,\n/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/78612/repo-new.png 1260w,\n/static/2780e1042ed7a0a74e2f0c3d8072cc01/db806/repo-new.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-1] GitHub Repository</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>레포지토리 이름은 [1-2]번 이미지처럼 본인의 username을 넣은 <strong>${username}.github.io</strong>로 작성해 주세요.\n이유는 개츠비 블로그 레포지토리로 사용할 겸 해당 레포지토리의 Discussions를 이용하기 위함이에요.\n그리고 Public을 선택해서 레포지토리를 생성해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/db806/create-new-repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.88607594936708%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-2] 레포지토리 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/f058b/create-new-repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/c26ae/create-new-repo.png 158w,\n/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/6bdcf/create-new-repo.png 315w,\n/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/f058b/create-new-repo.png 630w,\n/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/40601/create-new-repo.png 945w,\n/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/78612/create-new-repo.png 1260w,\n/static/1d2c3ce3a91ca2ce976430ec94681106/db806/create-new-repo.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-2] 레포지토리 생성</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>레포지토리를 생성했다면 <strong>Settings > General</strong>로 이동하여 <strong>Features 항목에 Discussions를 클릭</strong>해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/db806/checked-discussions.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 110.12658227848102%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-3] Discussions 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/f058b/checked-discussions.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/c26ae/checked-discussions.png 158w,\n/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/6bdcf/checked-discussions.png 315w,\n/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/f058b/checked-discussions.png 630w,\n/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/40601/checked-discussions.png 945w,\n/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/78612/checked-discussions.png 1260w,\n/static/df9463ec82b9b3e0a86e0aa4c6f3163b/db806/checked-discussions.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-3] Discussions 설정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>그리고 상단에 <strong>Discussions</strong>를 클릭 후, Categories 영역에 존재하는 <strong>연필 아이콘을 클릭</strong>해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/db806/discussions-tab.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.75949367088608%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-4] Discussions 카테고리 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/f058b/discussions-tab.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/c26ae/discussions-tab.png 158w,\n/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/6bdcf/discussions-tab.png 315w,\n/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/f058b/discussions-tab.png 630w,\n/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/40601/discussions-tab.png 945w,\n/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/78612/discussions-tab.png 1260w,\n/static/258fe6c9b882a70a08666e76bfb9c9d7/db806/discussions-tab.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-4] Discussions 카테고리 생성</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>New Category</strong> 버튼을 클릭해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/db806/new-category.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.75949367088608%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-5] 신규 카테고리 생성하기\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/f058b/new-category.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/c26ae/new-category.png 158w,\n/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/6bdcf/new-category.png 315w,\n/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/f058b/new-category.png 630w,\n/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/40601/new-category.png 945w,\n/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/78612/new-category.png 1260w,\n/static/1d9054580f6e34ec4f5ad5c2b61b9364/db806/new-category.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-5] 신규 카테고리 생성하기</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>카테고리 이름은 <strong>Comments</strong>로 작성하도록 하고, 포맷은 <strong>Announcement</strong>를 선택해서 카테고리를 생성해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/db806/create-category.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.92405063291139%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-6] 생성할 카테고리 정보 입력\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/f058b/create-category.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/c26ae/create-category.png 158w,\n/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/6bdcf/create-category.png 315w,\n/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/f058b/create-category.png 630w,\n/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/40601/create-category.png 945w,\n/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/78612/create-category.png 1260w,\n/static/13b477a2eb554aed836c20663efcf9b2/db806/create-category.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-6] 생성할 카테고리 정보 입력</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>Comments</strong>라는 카테고리가 생성된 걸 확인할 수 있어요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/db806/added-category.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.51898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1-7] 신규 카테고리 생성 완료\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/f058b/added-category.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/c26ae/added-category.png 158w,\n/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/6bdcf/added-category.png 315w,\n/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/f058b/added-category.png 630w,\n/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/40601/added-category.png 945w,\n/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/78612/added-category.png 1260w,\n/static/d2b9f682153360606c333ca4d36e49c7/db806/added-category.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1-7] 신규 카테고리 생성 완료</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>2. giscus 앱 설치 및 설정</h2>\n<p>Discussions 설정과 카테고리 생성까지 완료했으면, <a href=\"https://github.com/apps/giscus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">giscus 앱 설치 페이지</a>에서 <strong>Install 버튼을 클릭</strong>해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-1] giscus 앱 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/f058b/install-giscus-app.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/c26ae/install-giscus-app.png 158w,\n/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/6bdcf/install-giscus-app.png 315w,\n/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/f058b/install-giscus-app.png 630w,\n/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/40601/install-giscus-app.png 945w,\n/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/78612/install-giscus-app.png 1260w,\n/static/c91bc01ff00f086e4fb0d8fb5d4c8c2d/db806/install-giscus-app.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-1] giscus 앱 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><strong>Only select repositories</strong>를 선택하고, Discussions를 설정했던 레포지토리를 선택해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/db806/select-repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.41772151898735%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-2] 읽기 권한 레포지토리 선택\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/f058b/select-repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/c26ae/select-repo.png 158w,\n/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/6bdcf/select-repo.png 315w,\n/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/f058b/select-repo.png 630w,\n/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/40601/select-repo.png 945w,\n/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/78612/select-repo.png 1260w,\n/static/f0c7aff6aa6c63538ef2d36dcca10cdd/db806/select-repo.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-2] 읽기 권한 레포지토리 선택</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>giscus 앱 설치가 완료됐으면, <a href=\"https://giscus.app/ko\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">giscus 설정 페이지</a>로 접속해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 110.12658227848102%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-3] giscus 앱 설치 완료\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/f058b/setting-giscus-app.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/c26ae/setting-giscus-app.png 158w,\n/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/6bdcf/setting-giscus-app.png 315w,\n/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/f058b/setting-giscus-app.png 630w,\n/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/40601/setting-giscus-app.png 945w,\n/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/78612/setting-giscus-app.png 1260w,\n/static/223a6432522aa82bcd4feaf0ea938a12/db806/setting-giscus-app.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-3] giscus 앱 설치 완료</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>giscus 설정 페이지에서 생성한 저장소 이름을 입력해 주세요. 저장소 이름 형태는 <strong>${username}/${username}.github.io</strong> 입니다.<br>\n그리고 <strong>Discussion 제목이 페이지 경로를 포함</strong> 방법으로 선택하고, 카테고리는 위에서 생성한 <strong>Comments</strong> 카테고리를 선택해 주세요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/db806/giscus-setting-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.64556962025317%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-4] 레포지토리 이름, 연결 방식, 카테고리 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/f058b/giscus-setting-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/c26ae/giscus-setting-1.png 158w,\n/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/6bdcf/giscus-setting-1.png 315w,\n/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/f058b/giscus-setting-1.png 630w,\n/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/40601/giscus-setting-1.png 945w,\n/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/78612/giscus-setting-1.png 1260w,\n/static/f51ed118670716f43da0077432933dca/db806/giscus-setting-1.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-4] 레포지토리 이름, 연결 방식, 카테고리 설정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>본인이 사용하고자 하는 기능과 테마를 선택해 주세요. giscus 설정을 모두 완료하면 <strong>script</strong>가 설정에 맞춰 생성됩니다.<br>\n해당 script를 참고하여 개츠비 블로그에 댓글 기능을 적용할게요.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/db806/giscus-setting-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.62025316455697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-5] 기능, 테마 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/f058b/giscus-setting-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/c26ae/giscus-setting-2.png 158w,\n/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/6bdcf/giscus-setting-2.png 315w,\n/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/f058b/giscus-setting-2.png 630w,\n/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/40601/giscus-setting-2.png 945w,\n/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/78612/giscus-setting-2.png 1260w,\n/static/481a1eb18f3d53ef4ed6cf002d884e30/db806/giscus-setting-2.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-5] 기능, 테마 설정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>3. Gatsby Blog에 giscus 적용</h2>\n<p>이전 <a href=\"(https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/)\">포스트에서 만든 개츠비 블로그 프로젝트를 열어</a>주세요.<br>\n그리고 <strong>components</strong> 디렉터리 하위에 <strong>comments.js</strong> 파일을 생성 후, 아래 코드를 작성하고,\n[2-5]번 이미지에서 생성된 <code class=\"language-text\">data-repo</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">data-repo-id</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">data-category-id</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">data-reactions-enabled</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">data-input-position</code> 값을 넣어주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useEffect<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> useRef <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Comments</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> commentRef <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useRef</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> giscus <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"script\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> giscusConfig <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"src\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://giscus.app/client.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-repo\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-repo-id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-category\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Comments\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-category-id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-mapping\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pathname\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-strict\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-reactions-enabled\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-emit-metadata\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-input-position\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-theme\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"preferred_color_scheme\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-lang\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ko\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"data-loading\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"lazy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"crossorigin\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"anonymous\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"async\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">entries</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>giscusConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      giscus<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    commentRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>giscus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div ref<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>commentRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Comments</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/db806/added-giscus-script.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[3-1] comment.js 파일 생성 및 코드 작성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/f058b/added-giscus-script.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/c26ae/added-giscus-script.png 158w,\n/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/6bdcf/added-giscus-script.png 315w,\n/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/f058b/added-giscus-script.png 630w,\n/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/40601/added-giscus-script.png 945w,\n/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/78612/added-giscus-script.png 1260w,\n/static/7a8cff587dac34b44df2e0478a2e0d49/db806/added-giscus-script.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100